text: Ekaterina Makarova and Elena Vesnina were the defending champions, but lost to Hsieh Su-wei and Peng Shuai in the semifinals. Chan Hao-ching and Yang Zhaoxuan won the title, defeating Hsieh and Peng in the final, 4–6, 6–2, [10–6]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Dubai Tennis Championships - Doubles Women's Doubles
